  <Content>Suomi will be hosting a series of poetry events for everyone to enjoy. &lt;i&gt;&lt;b&gt;Come show off your wits when words and wine are mixed!&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt;  Each round will be broken down into three events: Short Themed Poem, Improv Poetry, and Partner Poetry Improv. The themes, and requirements will defer each round, so make sure you read each announcement thoroughly!

Each event will be judged separately, and prizes may be awarded based on participation. The purpose of these events are to inspire creativity and provide entertainment; do not expect or request for prizes. 


